\insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 She would have been about - approximately eighty if she'd been alive today. Approximately about eighty year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 And then Martha?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Martha -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Take Edith then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Well Edie's about seventy-seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Two years older than you, the same as Robert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Robert was - Robert would have been seventy-five. Two year older than me. R
