\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 What about your dad, did he have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh he's the same, we're all good }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 eaters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 
