\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Well we used to get second helpings, you know, more - more pot
atoes and cabbage and whatever it was. Get a second helping. And it's one thing she believed in - were getting the food down us. Aye. We were never started that way.
