\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh just - just eat what was put onto it. We were trained that way like. 'Cos on - when me d
ad was home and on the Sunday me dad used to practically the dinner and me dad sit at the end, head of the table as the saying is, we were all round. He used to cut all the joint up and put in on plates and dish the dinner out. He did all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 What somebody didn't eat anything they were given?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh well, it was just left like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 No fuss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh no. It }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 ' - 'course perhaps a little bit - telling off like, not - to get it eaten, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 But if you still didn't eat it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 No, you -
 well, it was just left you see. And what was left over, it used to be - warmed up for the next day. Used - fried potatoes what was left you see and just made a meal of it what we'd left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 If there was something on the table that you wanted like the salt or the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 
jug}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925  of water, id you sued to ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh yes. Pass the salt or water, we were taught that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Did you used to ask for second helpings or did you wait 'til they were offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 No, just used to say, could we have a little bit
 more mother or dad and - you know. You just got it. I think they were happy when they say we eaten it the way we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Were you taught to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 use}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
