\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh we just sat on the chair. We just sat on the chair and got on with the dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Did you ever bring any toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 No, no. 'Course we had toys to play with and that and books but we - never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 But you didn't bring them to table at mealtimes?
