\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 But the rest of the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918468 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 Oh me mum }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
