Oh yes. Sometimes - sometimes they used to - you know, the stools like that but we used to call 'em crockets, sometimes they just put a little bit meal on them and just sit on the floor beside the fire and just eat it off the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7674431\charrsid4459925 crocket}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 .
