Oh well, it's different - it's different those days it is now because in the private enterprise you see well you see you got the nationalized industries now, this was private enterprise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11365493 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13255302\charrsid4459925 What did you think about the time you were down the mine?
